Class StepFunctionArgsBaseListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.javaToAvalla.antlr.StepFunctionArgsBaseListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener, StepFunctionArgsListener
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    StepFunctionArgsListener

    public class StepFunctionArgsBaseListener
extends Object
implements StepFunctionArgsListener
    This class provides an empty implementation of StepFunctionArgsListener, which can be extended to create a listener which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
